---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import sunbul from "../../assets/sunbul.svg";
import uzum from "../../assets/uzum.svg";
import teker from "../../assets/teker.svg";
import whoWe from "../../assets/who-we.jpg";
---

<section class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-7.5 pt-6">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-22">
    <div class="lg:text-end">
      There are many variations of passages of Lorem Ipsum available, but the
      majority have suffered alteration in some form, by injected humour, or
      randomised words which don't look even slightly believable. If you are
      going to use a passage of Lorem Ipsum, you need to be sure there isn't
      anything embarrassing hidden in the middle of text. All the Lorem Ipsum
      generators on the Internet tend to repeat predefined chunks as necessary,
      making this the first true generator on the Internet.
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-end flex-wrap items-center gap-x-11 lg:gap-x-14 gap-y-2.5">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3.5">
        <Image
          src={sunbul}
          alt="sunbul"
          loading="eager"
          class="size-10 lg:size-12.5 ms-auto"
        />
        <h6 class="text-base tracking-wider text-[#363131]">
          Yüksək keyfiyyət
        </h6>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3.5">
        <Image
          src={uzum}
          alt="uzum"
          loading="eager"
          class="size-10 lg:size-12.5 ms-auto"
        />
        <h6 class="text-base tracking-wider text-[#363131]">Bol çeşid</h6>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3.5">
        <Image
          src={teker}
          alt="teker"
          loading="eager"
          class="size-10 lg:size-12.5 ms-auto"
        />
        <h6 class="text-base tracking-wider text-[#363131]">
          Bağlardan süfrənizə
        </h6>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <Image src={whoWe} alt="about" loading="eager" class="rounded-md" />
  </div>
</section>
